  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Main] \uFF1CDigi-Burst 3\uFF1E (Trash 3 of this Digimon's
    Digivolution cards to activate the effect below.)\u30FBYou may play 1 level 3
    purple Digimon card from your trash without paying its memory cost. Any [On Play]
    effects on Digimon played with this effect don't activate."
